Class BrokenRadar

java.lang.Object
BrokenRadar
public class BrokenRadar
extends java.lang.Object

BrokenRadar

The Broken Radar is a custome feature that allows the user to see some coordinates of the opponent's board marked by ships. However, since it's broken not all provided coordinates are true. One coordinate is random.
